WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:00.939
Pois bem,

2
00:00:00.980 --> 00:00:01.769
meus caros

3
00:00:01.909 --> 00:00:03.150
conseguiram aí fechar

4
00:00:03.740 --> 00:00:04.179
Tranquilo,

5
00:00:04.260 --> 00:00:04.469
né?

6
00:00:04.789 --> 00:00:05.739
Não é tão complexo.

7
00:00:05.780 --> 00:00:07.099
Vamos lá a nossa resposta

8
00:00:07.340 --> 00:00:08.460
